		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Buffalo</placeName> <add>&#63;</add> <date>17 <add>Hebrew</add> 5614</date></p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><add>Hebrew</add></p>
				<p>Revd</p>
				<p><addressee>Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">Sir&#33;</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Your Book&#44; with the Books<lb/> I recd from <persName>Mr. E. J. Bernheim</persName>&#44; and paid<lb/> the freight for on it&#44; and also the carriage&#44;<lb/> only&#44; I can&#39;t make you <sic>aquinted</sic> how<lb/> it will be&#44; with the delivery&#44; this moment<lb/> when I write to you&#44; I have said<add>&#63;</add> to <persName>E. J.<lb/> Bernheim</persName>&#44; if he want <hi rend="underline">one</hi>&#44; but he did<lb/> not answer&#44; no doubt you know the<lb/> nature of those <add>&#63;</add>&#44; as they are<lb/> a <add>Hebrew</add>.  I can not keep <add>&#63;</add> any longer&#44;<lb/> as I have&#44; so much writing&#44; and dis&#44;<lb/>pute in your Occident&#44; on account<lb/> of <persName>Dr. Wises</persName> writing and in particular<lb/> <persName>Mr Revd Dr Illowy</persName> how D<add>&#63;</add> him&#33; let<lb/> me stop&#44; all those disputes&#44; I have a<lb/> valuable Book printed&#44; by a great <add>Hebrew</add><lb/> calld&#44; <add>Hebrew</add>&#44; and <persName>Mr Lane</persName> writes only a few<lb/> words&#44; <sic>wich</sic> will make <sic>betwen</sic> those two<lb/> D<hi rend="underline">rs</hi>. And he <sic>explain</sic> himself&#44; with a for<lb/>wards <add>Hebrew</add><lb/> 86<lb/> <add>Hebrew</add><lb/> 86 and according all <add>Hebrew</add> upon our <add>Hebrew</add><lb/> the whole creation&#44; <del>was</del> came in existence <add>Hebrew</add><lb/> and no doubt&#44; every learned man knows&#44;<lb/> that <add>Hebrew</add><lb/> at present I have but 2 scholars&#44; the children&#44;<lb/> of <persName>Mr <add>&#63;</add> Noah</persName>&#44; but in <add>&#63;</add> of time I may<lb/> let come some more as I keep school only<lb/> for a pass time.</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p rend="align(center)">Sir&#33;</p>
				<p>I have wrote to <persName>Dr Wise</persName> the same<lb/> but he did not answer me&#44; tis&#44;<lb/> as I know&#44; the has a little <sic>enamo&#44;<lb/>sity</sic> against me&#44; on account of a<lb/> <add>Hebrew</add> who he gave <add>Hebrew</add> and freedom<lb/> to perform the service Duties appertain&#44;<lb/>ning our Holy <hi rend="underline">Religion</hi>.  I will not<lb/> detain you&#44;k with much writing&#44; as I<lb/> know&#44; you can employ your time<lb/> to other purposes&#44; but I thought<lb/> you might show my letter to<lb/> <persName>Dr <sic>Ellowy</sic></persName> and I hope that the<lb/> gentleman will be satisfied</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Remain yours</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">Respectfully</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)"><add>&#63;</add></p>
				<p>P. S.</p>
				<p>I must make you <sic>aquainted</sic> with<lb/> that&#44; I don&#39;t perform no more<lb/> <placeName>Italy</placeName><add>&#63;</add> services in the Synagogue.<lb/> and this quarrel is nothing to me.<lb/> but&#44; for the sake of <add>Hebrew</add> between<lb/> <sic>booth</sic> parties&#44; I have mentioned to you<lb/> the writing of <add>&#63;</add><lb/> <add>Hebrew</add><lb/> and<lb/> <placeName><hi rend="underline">Amsterdam</hi></placeName></p>
